The Block Australia Fans vs Faves Series 8 Episode 58

The Block is back with a Fans versus Favorites format - will the old hands prevail?

With only hours until tools down, the teams race to finish the interiors of the two challenge houses. But before the judges get to cast their eye over the finished houses, the teams check out each other's work and have their opinion.
